public class CallData
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This is a simple Call data carrier used for call snapshot delivery from dynamic or throttled TelephonyProviders.

The state given should be of type Call state public final variables. Creation date: (2000-06-15 14:05:44)
